lead_paragraph: The Blue Jays are installing a dirt infield at the Rogers Centre for the first time but say it is too early to determine whether they would replace artificial turf with grass in some future season.

headline.print_headline: Blue Jays Will Have Dirt Infield in Time for Coming Season
